stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> HELD: POST /jobs (upload)
    HELD --> RELEASED: POST /jobs/id/release
    HELD --> CANCELLED: DELETE /jobs/id
    RELEASED --> PROCESSING: Worker picks up from SQS
    PROCESSING --> DONE: Print completes
    PROCESSING --> FAILED: Unrecoverable error
    PROCESSING --> PROCESSING: Crash → SQS redeliver → re-process
    DONE --> [*]
    CANCELLED --> [*]
    FAILED --> [*]
